attributionInfo.agentName: Jennie & Eddie Luxury Living Boston Team

description: OFFER ACCEPTED. OPEN HOUSE CANCELED.  Welcome to this beautifully renovated one-bedroom residence at Dockside Place, where historic character meets modern sophistication. This thoughtfully updated home features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and custom closets. Exposed brick walls, soaring ceilings, and oversized windows create an airy atmosphere with a touch of industrial charm. The spacious open-concept layout includes a stunning kitchen with a large island—ideal for entertaining. The bedroom is spacious and features both a walk-in closet and a secondary closet, each outfitted with custom shelving. The bathroom includes a beautifully tiled shower with glass doors, linen storage, and radiant floor heating for added comfort. Enjoy the convenience of central heating and cooling as well an in-unit laundry. Seller welcomes offers with requests for buyer concessions.
